          <ul class="text-red-200 space-y-2 text-sm">
            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="w-1 h-1 bg-red-400 rounded-full mr-2 mt-2"></span>Selektivna podloga za uzgoj mikobakterija</li>
            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="w-1 h-1 bg-red-400 rounded-full mr-2 mt-2"></span>Sadrži krumpirovo brašno kao glavni izvor hranjivih tvari</li>
            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="w-1 h-1 bg-red-400 rounded-full mr-2 mt-2"></span>Malahitno zelenilo inhibira rast kontaminantnih bakterija</li>
            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="w-1 h-1 bg-red-400 rounded-full mr-2 mt-2"></span>Dodaju se svježa jaja za povećanje hranjivih svojstava</li>
            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="w-1 h-1 bg-red-400 rounded-full mr-2 mt-2"></span>Sterilizira se na 121°C/30 min</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-blue-500/20 border border-blue-500/30 rounded-lg p-4">
          <p class="text-blue-300 font-semibold">
          <strong class="text-blue-200">Primjena:</strong> uzgoj Mycobacterium phei i drugih mikobakterija u praktikumskoj nastavi
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    `,
